# Docker Quick Start

### Dependencies

```
docker run -d -p 80:80 docker/getting-started
Run command below in command prompt to check installation
```

# Docker Quick Start

### Dependencies

```
Navigate to docker
Windows: bottom right hand menu
```

# Docker Quick Start

### Dependencies

```
“Getting-started” container will auto-generate a random name
Select open in browser icon
```

# Docker Quick Start

### Dependencies

```
If browser loads “Getting started” page, install is successful
