# Compose application

### Dependencies

```
Run command below in command prompt to change directory
cd documents\github\cosc4012020\cd_spec_viewer_web
```

# Compose application

### Dependencies

```
Run command below in command prompt to build container
docker-compose -f docker-compose.yml build
```

# Run application

### Dependencies

```
Run command below in command prompt to run container
docker-compose -f docker-compose.yml up
```

# Access application

### Dependencies

```
Navigate to Docker GUI and start application
```

# Access application

